## Examine Messages
plankton-harvester-examine-power = The harvester is [color=cyan]{$status}[/color].
plankton-harvester-examine-container-empty = No sample container loaded. Insert a container to collect plankton.
plankton-harvester-examine-cooldown = Next harvest in {$time} seconds.
plankton-harvester-examine-ready = Ready to harvest!
plankton-harvester-examine-harvesting = {$time} seconds until the plankton is ready.

## Interaction Messages
plankton-harvester-container-inserted = Container loaded into harvester.
plankton-harvester-success = A new colony has been harvested!
plankton-harvester-no-atmosphere = No atmosphere detected in pipes.
plankton-harvester-insufficient-seawater = Insufficient Seawater.
